*docker
		

    Install the Docker service package with your favorite tool

    Start the Docker service

    Search for an appropriate image from Docker Hub or your private repository

    Pull the image

    Run the image

    And finally, test the application.


 *comandos docker 
 	$ docker <command> --help

 	-arrancar contenedor
 	docker run

 	-crear contenedor
 	docker create

 	-borrar contenedor 
 	$ docker rm $(docker ps -a -q)
	
	-instalacion
	apt-get install docker.io
	
	-buscar imagenes 
	docker search nombreimagen
	
	-descargar contenedores
	docker pull nombreimagen
	
	-listar imagenes
	docker images 
	
	-listar imagenes con mas  detalles 
	docker images --all
	
	-servicio 
	service docker start

        
